trans-unit.source: SAP Analytics Cloud allows you to use SAP HANA Smart Data Integration (SDI) and its Data Provisioning Agent to enable Linked Dimensions and query blending between models based off Data Import connections, and models based off Live Data connections to your own SAP HANA system. This requires that you first download and install the SDI Data Provisioning agent to a network location from which it can establish HTTPS connections to SAP Analytics Cloud, and JDBC connections to your SAP HANA system. For installation instructions, see the {0}.
